#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-cvslastlog.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints the log entry for the last commit for a file."
msgstr "सञ्चिकायाः कृते अन्तिम-प्रतिबद्धतायाः कृते लॉग्-प्रविष्टिं मुद्रयति ।"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-cvslastlog.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cvslastlog</command> <group><option><replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>cvslastlog इति</command><group><option><replaceable> सञ्चिकानाम</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cvslastlog.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cvslastlog.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cvslastlog</command> shows the log associated with the last CVS "
"commit for the given file. It depends on the version of the local file, not "
"the one on the server."
msgstr ""
"<command>cvslastlog</command> दत्तसञ्चिकायाः अन्तिम CVS commit इत्यनेन सह सम्बद्धं "
"लॉग् दर्शयति । स्थानीयसञ्चिकायाः संस्करणस्य उपरि निर्भरं भवति, न तु सर्वरे विद्यमानस्य ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cvslastlog.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"
